    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 55241.0,
      "end_time": 56074.0,
      "text": "And the thing is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 56074.0,
      "end_time": 59418.0,
      "text": "if you've got an abundance\nof a particular resource,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 59418.0,
      "end_time": 62453.0,
      "text": "than it makes complete\nsense to make the most of it"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 62453.0,
      "end_time": 64161.0,
      "text": "and utilise it to help you out"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 64161.0,
      "end_time": 65531.0,
      "text": "with what you're trying to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 65531.00000000001,
      "end_time": 69007.0,
      "text": "So, that's exactly what we're\ndoing through using grass."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 69007.0,
      "end_time": 72568.0,
      "text": "So, if you live in suburbia,\nthan the likelihood is"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 72568.0,
      "end_time": 76329.0,
      "text": "that there's gonna be a lot\nof people mowing their lawns."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 76329.0,
      "end_time": 79822.0,
      "text": "So, all you need to do is ask\nthem for their law clippings."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 79822.0,
      "end_time": 82603.0,
      "text": "And even just volunteer\nto pick them up yourself."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 82603.0,
      "end_time": 85832.0,
      "text": "Because they are such an\nabundant resource around there."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 85832.0,
      "end_time": 87804.0,
      "text": "And the thing is you\ncan get them for free."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 87804.0,
      "end_time": 89169.0,
      "text": "And when it comes to mulching,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 89169.0,
      "end_time": 91207.0,
      "text": "what you wanna do is place a two inch"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 91207.0,
      "end_time": 93533.0,
      "text": "or a five to six centimetre layer."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 93533.0,
      "end_time": 95357.0,
      "text": "You can make the layer thicker"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 95357.0,
      "end_time": 99497.0,
      "text": "but that's kind of a\ngood minimum to aim for."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 99497.0,
      "end_time": 100510.0,
      "text": "On our small holding,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 100510.0,
      "end_time": 102586.0,
      "text": "we do have a lot of land."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 102586.0,
      "end_time": 104145.0,
      "text": "So, that means a lot of grass."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 104145.0,
      "end_time": 104978.0,
      "text": "So, at the moment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 104978.0,
      "end_time": 107037.0,
      "text": "we're currently scything our orchard"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 107037.0,
      "end_time": 109480.0,
      "text": "and that's gonna create\nso much hay for us."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 109480.0,
      "end_time": 111188.0,
      "text": "Now, there is something about hay"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 111188.0,
      "end_time": 113318.0,
      "text": "which people like to bring up a lot."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 113318.0,
      "end_time": 114722.0,
      "text": "And I saw it in a few comments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 114722.0,
      "end_time": 117340.0,
      "text": "in the growing the potatoes the lazy way."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 117340.0,
      "end_time": 119841.0,
      "text": "Where we simply placed\npotatoes on the ground"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 119841.0,
      "end_time": 123671.0,
      "text": "and just covered it with\na thick layer of hay."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 123671.0,
      "end_time": 125170.0,
      "text": "And people saying that you're basically"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 125170.0,
      "end_time": 127059.0,
      "text": "just putting down grass seed."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 127059.0,
      "end_time": 128138.0,
      "text": "And that is true."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 128138.0,
      "end_time": 130226.0,
      "text": "We have a wildflower hay meadow."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 130226.0,
      "end_time": 132828.0,
      "text": "And when we have hay, we like to cut it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 132828.0,
      "end_time": 136564.0,
      "text": "after all the wildflowers have seeded."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 136564.0,
      "end_time": 139453.0,
      "text": "And in that case, there\nis quite a lot of seed."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 139453.0,
      "end_time": 141371.0,
      "text": "But the idea behind mulch"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 141371.0,
      "end_time": 144849.0,
      "text": "and going towards no dig garden system"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 144849.0,
      "end_time": 145897.0,
      "text": "is that you're just going to"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 145897.0,
      "end_time": 148431.0,
      "text": "continue piling it on over the year."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 148431.0,
      "end_time": 150328.0,
      "text": "Yes, hay can give you a lot of weeds"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 150328.0,
      "end_time": 153979.0,
      "text": "and it can give you a lot\nof grass to deal with."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 153979.0,
      "end_time": 155715.0,
      "text": "But that's basically only"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 155715.0,
      "end_time": 158493.0,
      "text": "if you take the hay off to leave bare soil"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 158493.0,
      "end_time": 160589.0,
      "text": "and then all the grass will grow through."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 160589.0,
      "end_time": 164044.0,
      "text": "Because the idea, with\nadopting a mulch system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 164044.0,
      "end_time": 165406.0,
      "text": "is that over the year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 165406.0,
      "end_time": 169148.0,
      "text": "you're going to continue placing\nsome more layers of mulch."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 169148.0,
      "end_time": 172160.0,
      "text": "And especially for something\nquite dense, such as hay."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 172160.0,
      "end_time": 174006.0,
      "text": "Especially after it's rained."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 174006.0,
      "end_time": 176139.0,
      "text": "It's literally going\nto smother the ground."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 176139.0,
      "end_time": 179762.0,
      "text": "So, the weeds will find it\nvery difficult to go through."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 179762.0,
      "end_time": 182242.0,
      "text": "And should any weeds\nhappen to come through,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 182242.0,
      "end_time": 184959.0,
      "text": "then it's so easy to pull out by hand."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 184959.0,
      "end_time": 188879.0,
      "text": "Or you can simply place another\nthick layer over the top."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 188879.0,
      "end_time": 191089.0,
      "text": "And gradually, as you build the layers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 191089.0,
      "end_time": 192170.0,
      "text": "the hay at the bottom,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 192170.0,
      "end_time": 194539.0,
      "text": "is going to start to break down."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 194539.0,
      "end_time": 196715.0,
      "text": "And it's going to release those nutrients."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 196715.0,
      "end_time": 198255.0,
      "text": "And as an interesting discussion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 198255.0,
      "end_time": 199643.0,
      "text": "where you're looking at,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 199643.0,
      "end_time": 201292.0,
      "text": "should I mulch with straw?"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 201292.0,
      "end_time": 202999.0,
      "text": "Or should I mulch with hay?"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 202999.0,
      "end_time": 204471.0,
      "text": "And yeah, straw has its benefits"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 204471.0,
      "end_time": 205956.0,
      "text": "because you might not get weeds"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 205956.0,
      "end_time": 208886.0,
      "text": "because they've already\ntaken the wheat off it."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 208886.0,
      "end_time": 211158.0,
      "text": "But the thing about hay is"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 211158.0,
      "end_time": 214269.0,
      "text": "that usually, especially\nfrom a wildflower hay meadow,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 214269.0,
      "end_time": 216686.0,
      "text": "or organically farmed meadow,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 217874.0,
      "end_time": 219292.0,
      "text": "there's other things growing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 219292.0,
      "end_time": 221587.0,
      "text": "apart from grass, such as clover."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 221587.0,
      "end_time": 224383.0,
      "text": "So, there actually tends to\nbe more nutrients in hay."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 224383.0,
      "end_time": 226378.0,
      "text": "So, if you want fertile soil,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 226378.0,
      "end_time": 229635.0,
      "text": "then what I'd recommend\nyou do is mulch with hay."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 229635.0,
      "end_time": 231386.0,
      "text": "And I can speak from experience"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 231386.0,
      "end_time": 234325.0,
      "text": "because this is the third year\nnow where we're using hay."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 234325.0,
      "end_time": 238090.0,
      "text": "And we haven't seen any\nnoticeable differences in weeds."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 238090.0,
      "end_time": 241845.0,
      "text": "In fact, by mulching more,\nwe are building more soil."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 241845.0,
      "end_time": 244062.0,
      "text": "And we're also weeding less."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 244062.0,
      "end_time": 246663.0,
      "text": "So, it's actually saving time."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 246663.0,
      "end_time": 248760.0,
      "text": "And if you happen to have a lot of hay"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 248760.0,
      "end_time": 251630.0,
      "text": "and you want to create\na new area of garden,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 251630.0,
      "end_time": 254484.0,
      "text": "then here's a great way\nto create a noted garden."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 254484.0,
      "end_time": 256562.0,
      "text": "All you need to do is take off"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 256562.0,
      "end_time": 258815.0,
      "text": "the top two to three inches,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 258815.0,
      "end_time": 261926.0,
      "text": "so around six to seven\ncentimetres of soil,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 261926.0,
      "end_time": 265539.0,
      "text": "and you place a really\nthick layer of hay on top."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 265539.0,
      "end_time": 267323.0,
      "text": "And then, with the soil\nthat you've taken off,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 267323.0,
      "end_time": 269585.0,
      "text": "you put that back onto the hay."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 269585.0,
      "end_time": 271697.0,
      "text": "And then, over time, this will break down"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 271697.0,
      "end_time": 273288.0,
      "text": "and then you can plant into this."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 273288.0,
      "end_time": 275005.0,
      "text": "And then, as the plants grow,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 275005.0,
      "end_time": 277427.0,
      "text": "then mulch around them with hay."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 277427.0,
      "end_time": 279546.0,
      "text": "And if you live in dry climate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 279546.0,
      "end_time": 281889.0,
      "text": "then mulching is a fantastic way"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 281889.0,
      "end_time": 283641.0,
      "text": "to reduce the need to water."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 283641.0,
      "end_time": 285463.0,
      "text": "But it acts as insulation"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 285463.0,
      "end_time": 288093.0,
      "text": "where it retains moisture within the soil."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 288093.0,
      "end_time": 290342.0,
      "text": "So, that's a really good benefit to it."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 290342.0,
      "end_time": 292571.0,
      "text": "One thing we did to demonstrate"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 292571.0,
      "end_time": 295406.0,
      "text": "the effectiveness of growing in hay bales,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 295406.0,
      "end_time": 299830.0,
      "text": "was that we kind of copied\nthe straw bale garden idea."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 299830.0,
      "end_time": 301976.0,
      "text": "We planted directly into hay bales"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 301976.0,
      "end_time": 303675.0,
      "text": "and we found two things."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 303675.0,
      "end_time": 305699.0,
      "text": "We found if you left a hay bale out"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 305699.0,
      "end_time": 307355.0,
      "text": "for a whole grain season,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 307355.0,
      "end_time": 309141.0,
      "text": "and then planted the next season,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 309141.0,
      "end_time": 312325.0,
      "text": "this would be the most\neffective thing to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 312325.0,
      "end_time": 313492.0,
      "text": "And the second thing is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 313492.0,
      "end_time": 316244.0,
      "text": "we didn't have to weed\nthe squash plants once."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 316244.0,
      "end_time": 317143.0,
      "text": "It was so simple."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 317143.0,
      "end_time": 319041.0,
      "text": "It was putting out a bale of hay,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 319041.0,
      "end_time": 320569.0,
      "text": "leaving it there for a year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 320569.0,
      "end_time": 322791.0,
      "text": "and then the following grain season,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 322791.0,
      "end_time": 324161.0,
      "text": "putting in a bit of compost,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 324161.0,
      "end_time": 326529.0,
      "text": "planting the plant, and then leaving it."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 326529.0,
      "end_time": 329740.0,
      "text": "And all we had to do was harvest\nit at the end of the year."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 329740.0,
      "end_time": 331280.0,
      "text": "And that's a prime example"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 331280.0,
      "end_time": 334104.0,
      "text": "that you can easily grow a lot of food"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 334104.0,
      "end_time": 337420.0,
      "text": "for hardly enough effort at all."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 337420.0,
      "end_time": 339375.0,
      "text": "I hope this video has inspired you a bit"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 339375.0,
